criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age > 18 years;

          -  Ph+/BCR-ABL+ CML in any phase of disease;

          -  Conception/pregnancy while diagnosed with CML

          -  Treatment with TKIs (before or after pregnancy);

          -  Signed written informed consent according to ICH/EU/GCP and national local laws.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient < 18 years

          -  Patients that suffer from any condition or illness that could prevent the patient to
             participate
